diff --git a/CHANGELOG.md b/CHANGELOG.md
index e827900..6e6f14c 100644
--- a/CHANGELOG.md
+++ b/CHANGELOG.md
@@ -1,3 +1,8 @@
+## [0.9.4] - 2026-07-11
+
+### Fixed
+- **Linux Self-Update Stuck on v0.9.2** — Fixed a bug where the bundled `shibaclaw/updater/update_manifest.json` was not bumped alongside releases, causing `_get_version()` to report a stale version (0.9.2) even after a successful `pip`/`pipx` upgrade to a newer release. This made the updater perpetually report "update available" without ever converging. Version resolution for pip installations now prefers installed package metadata (`importlib.metadata`) over the bundled manifest, ensuring the reported version always reflects the actually-installed wheel version.
+
 ## [0.9.3] - 2025-01-15
 
 ### Fixed
